data.description: ANOTHER PRICE REDUCTION ON THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME! Check out this new style home nestled in beautiful Meadowville Landing. This Energy Star home also offers 4 BRs, 2.5 baths, gourmet kitchen with large island & breakfast nook, 9 feet ceilings & 3 car garage. Enjoy Autumn evenings on the private backyard patio and when it gets too chilly, step inside to snuggle up in your luxurious two-story great room. But it doesn’t stop there! If you're looking to relax, socialize or get in a quick workout, the gorgeous like-new pool, fitness center and clubhouse are just down the street. Or enjoy some peace and quiet as you stroll the paths that wind around the ponds and bank of the James River.  You are just minutes from the exciting new Lego facility as well as I-295 and I-95, making commuting a breeze! qualified buyers, MOTIVATED SELLERS, PLEASE MAKE OFFER NOW!
